    "Heuristic prompts are especially useful for tasks that involve disambiguation, extraction, or classification of entities or relations. 3.",
    "Chain of thought prompts are also effective for guiding the LLM to produce logical and coherent outputs.",
    "These prompts use a multistep approach to generate sentences that contain a series of questions and answers that resolve the task in the context.",
    "Chain of thought prompts are especially useful for tasks that involve reasoning, inference, or coreference resolution. 4.",
